---
import { completedProjects, ongoingProjects } from '../../data/projects';

const totalProjects = completedProjects.length + ongoingProjects.length;
---

<section id="about" class="py-32 px-6 relative z-10">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <p class="section-eyebrow mx-auto">About</p>
      <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black gradient-text mt-6 mb-4">Built For Analytics That Teams Can Use</h2>
      <p class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        I like building clean reporting systems, dependable ETL flows, and AI-assisted tools that move beyond prototypes and actually support operations.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="relative order-2 md:order-1">
        <div class="glass rounded-[2rem] p-8 md:p-10 max-w-md mx-auto md:ml-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <div class="w-28 h-28 mx-auto mb-6 glass rounded-3xl p-4 border border-white/50">
              <img src="/images/profile.jpg" alt="Vinod M" class="w-full h-full rounded-2xl object-cover" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold gradient-text mb-2">Vinod M</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 font-semibold">Data Analytics Developer</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center">
            <div class="metric-card px-3 py-4">
              <div class="text-3xl font-black gradient-text">{totalProjects}+</div>
              <div class="text-slate-500 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.16em]">Projects</div>
            </div>
            <div class="metric-card px-3 py-4">
              <div class="text-3xl font-black gradient-text">3</div>
              <div class="text-slate-500 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.16em]">Live Dashboards</div>
            </div>
            <div class="metric-card px-3 py-4">
              <div class="text-3xl font-black gradient-text">MCA</div>
              <div class="text-slate-500 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.16em]">Graduate</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-6 rounded-[1.5rem] bg-slate-900 px-5 py-5 text-left text-white">
            <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-teal-300">Current Positioning</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold">Data Analyst . BI Engineer . Analytics Developer</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="order-1 md:order-2 space-y-6 max-w-xl">
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-800 leading-relaxed">
          I work at the point where <span class="gradient-text font-semibold">analytics engineering</span>, reporting, and applied AI meet.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          My recent experience includes building Python ETL pipelines, Streamlit KPI dashboards, validation queries in SQL, and automated reporting workflows for operational teams.
        </p>

        <div class="glass p-6 rounded-[1.6rem] border border-teal-700/10">
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed font-medium">
            At <strong>VisionVerse Technology</strong>, I improved data accuracy by 25 percent and reduced reporting effort by 30 percent through ETL automation and dashboard delivery.
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          During my internship at <strong>Qikk Automation Technology (Rexsatronics), Koorgally</strong>, I prepared validated NLP datasets, trained an NER model to 92 percent accuracy, and supported transformer-based key-value extraction work.
        </p>

        <div class="glass p-6 rounded-[1.6rem] border border-emerald-700/10">
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed font-medium">
            I am the <strong>Co-founder of Medhaksha Technology</strong>.
            <a href="https://medhakshatech.in/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="ml-2 text-teal-700 hover:text-slate-950 underline underline-offset-4 transition-colors duration-300">
              medhakshatech.in
            </a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="glass rounded-[1.6rem] p-5">
            <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-orange-700">Flagged Project</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">GRS Fantasy Park MIS Command Center</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">Revenue, footfall, forecasting, anomaly alerts, and KPI reporting in one dashboard.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="glass rounded-[1.6rem] p-5">
            <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-teal-700">Published Work</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">IJIRCCE Research Publication</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">Object detection, tracking, and speed estimation for real-time monitoring.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          I am currently seeking a <strong>data analytics, BI, or applied AI role</strong> where I can contribute production-ready dashboarding and data pipeline work from day one.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
